    <item>
      <title>比莉·艾利什支持哈里斯，乔·罗根称赞她的辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/billie-eilish-joe-rogan-add-to-celebrity-support-for-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在副总统和唐纳德·特朗普都在极其激烈的选举竞争的最后几周争夺首次投票者的选票之际，两位对不同派别的年轻美国人具有吸引力的一些名人增加了对卡玛拉·哈里斯的名人支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/billie-eilish-joe-rogan-add-to-celebrity-support-for-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 19:26:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯寻求将工薪家庭的儿童保育费用限制在 7% 以内</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/harris-seeks-to-cap-child-care-costs-at-7-for-working-families</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯表示，她将寻求将工薪家庭的儿童保育费用限制在其收入的 7% 以内，这是她向选民保证将解决高昂物价和普遍的经济焦虑问题的最新举措，这些问题一直威胁着她与共和党人唐纳德·特朗普的总统竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/harris-seeks-to-cap-child-care-costs-at-7-for-working-families</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 19:25:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普承诺恢复他曾取消的 SALT 减免和税收优惠</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/trump-pledges-to-restore-salt-write-off-the-tax-break-he-curbed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将恢复州和地方税减免政策，这是纽约人喜爱的一项减税政策，前总统特朗普在白宫任职期间曾限制过这项政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/trump-pledges-to-restore-salt-write-off-the-tax-break-he-curbed</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 19:22:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>微软称拜登退出竞选后俄罗斯影响力运动转向哈里斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/russian-election-propaganda-targets-harris-microsoft-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[微软公司的最新研究显示，在总统乔·拜登结束重返白宫的竞选活动后，俄罗斯影响美国大选的行动转向利用篡改和误导性视频抹黑副总统卡马拉·哈里斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/russian-election-propaganda-targets-harris-microsoft-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黎巴嫩传呼机爆炸事件引发人们对破坏方法的猜测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/exploding-pagers-in-lebanon-spur-theories-on-methods-of-sabotage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从星期二寻呼机在黎巴嫩全境爆发的那一刻起，各种理论开始流传，认为这种在世界许多地方被视为过时的设备如何被改造成危险武器，造成数人死亡，近 3,000 人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/exploding-pagers-in-lebanon-spur-theories-on-methods-of-sabotage</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 18:36:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>真主党称以色列策划了黎巴嫩传呼机爆炸事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/pagers-in-lebanon-blast-including-hezbollah</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗支持的真主党指责以色列策划了这次袭击，造成黎巴嫩境内多人死亡，近 3,000 人受伤，这加剧了人们对爆发全面战争的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/pagers-in-lebanon-blast-including-hezbollah</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 14:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
